📚 Theory Content
2.2 Regression vs Classification

Aspect	     |         Regression	           |     Classification

Target	     |         Continuous value	     |     Discrete class

Example	     |         House price	         |     Spam detection

Output	     |         e.g., $250,000	       |     e.g., Spam/Not Spam

Evaluation	 |         MSE, MAE, R²	         |     Accuracy, Precision, Recall

Algorithms	 |         Linear Regression,SVR |     Logistic Regression, KNN
